g us are facts.  We can choose to believe whatever we want.  Personally I think that whatever the 4 pet rule might be it's affect on the actual game is totally insignificant.  IE there is nothing to be gained by planning attacks around the limitation.  It's not a good idea to limit the number of pets on a mob to 4. <p><center>
